  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Automated titration of propofol and remifentanil guided by the bispectral index (BIS) has
      been used for numerous surgical procedures. Orthotopic liver transplantation (OLT) uniquely
      combines major volaemic changes, an anhepatic phase, and ischaemia-reperfusion syndrome. We
      assessed the behaviour of this automated controller during OLT
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
